title: Wison on the Lake House for rent
posting_body: ['167 Ontario Street, Wilson NY 14172', 'Location, Location, Location:', 'The location is perfect!', 'The house is located right on the shore of Lake Ontario where you can see the skyline of Toronto by just walking out the lake side 16 foot sliding glass doors.', ' This location is one of the few in the world where you can see the sunrise out of the water and sunset in the water right from the lakeside deck.', 'It is wonderful to enter a relaxing small town atmosphere yet still have access to several activities, attractions, restaurants and shops as you would in a city.', 'The home is located across the street from the bustling Wilson Boathouse Restaurant, a quaint upscale restaurant.', 'Several small shops surround the incredible Wilson Harbor all just steps away right across the street.', ' Brownies Ice Cream stand is just a short walk away as well.', ' If you want to partake in the incredible fishing of Lake Ontario, several charters are available or just walk a block down the street to the wonderful Wilson Pier and drop a line.', ' We appreciate this home’s proximity to Canada as well as the neighboring U.S. cities such as Lockport, Lewiston, Niagara Falls & Buffalo (quick access to Canada can be made via the Lewiston-Queenston Bridge.', 'Fort Niagara is a short drive away on route 18 in Youngstown, NY a nice quiet drive along Lake Ontario.']

title: Unique long term rental, great location but rough area
posting_body: ['Entire House.', ' Unique long term rental in great location but rough neighborhood-near ECMC.', 'Remote owners seek right person to secure property in disrepair, live in house initially for 6 mo for reduced rent w/min 5 hour weekly commitment to clean up then fix-up property.', 'You pay waste, electric/gas-we pay water.', '*', 'PLEASE READ.', '\xa0 Please show us, that you are good to work with, by following this simple instruction.', '\xa0* Please provide phone number.', '\xa0* We will not engage via text.', '*', 'Property is livable but needs fixing up.', '\xa0 If you want a whole house, \xa0help us by demonstrating verified regular progress then we will extend rental agreement.', 'Initially work will be clean up, fix window, front steps.', 'You MUST pass background check after meeting on video, provide $850 security.', ' You pay electric, gas, waste, we pay water.', ' Quoted rent amount is for ONE person.', ' No arrangement for catching up on deposit, getting in door.', 'You can move in and start but evidence of work must be provided.', 'No excuses like had busy week or sick but show regular progress.', "If not, won't work out, as house once remedied commands higher rent, but will hold it down on negotiated basis in appreciation: you treat us good, we ll do same.", "Money only isn't our main concern but security."]

title: 3BR directly across from Dyouville | MUST SEE INSIDE!
posting_body: ['Available for Fall!', " 3br in a great college area rental directly across from D'youville.", 'UPDATED BRAND NEW MODERN APARTMENT with all electric and plumbing replaced.', ' Kitchen and bathroom gutted and remodeled.', '- Three (3) bedroom second (2nd) floor UPPER', '- $1695/mo (~$565/room for 3 person occupancy) + utilities (gas, elec and internet approx $200-300/mo total)', '- Brand new HIGH END kitchen (dishwasher, microwave, Corian countertops)', '- Brand new HIGH END bathroom (classic subway tile, rainfall shower/tub)', '- Partially furnished (bed, couch, chairs, furniture, appliances)', '- FREE Laundry in basement', 'DIRECTLY ACROSS from SASE* on Prospect Ave.  Well-lit, community street parking with just a literal ONE (1) minute walk to class and library every day.', ' Only a 5 minute drive downtown, walk to stores and restaurants, school - 20 min to everywhere!', ' Dyouville college campus area, but better that living on campus!', ' Quiet, respectful neighbors downstairs and we ask the same of you.', '6, 9 or 12 mo lease ok.', 'Apartment available August 15th.', 'No pets, No smoking, Street parking only.', ' References required.', '***SASE - The Dr. Charles and Mary Schweitzer Bauer School of Arts, Science and Education (SASE) building is the home to 19 labs, 9 state-of-the-art smart classrooms, faculty offices, and the primary home to a number of academic studies.', 'The 85,000 square foot building was built in 2015 and it is a combination of new, modern spaces and the classic architecture of the former Letchworth family mansion, which was built in 1890.', 'Throughout the building you’ll find smartly crafted nooks and spaces designed for studying alone and in groups, and on the second floor you’ll discover one of our most popular study spaces in the atrium with bright, sunny views of the neighborhood (and your NEW apartment!) and easily configurable furniture to accompany any size study group.', 'On the first floor is Saint’s Café, where you can grab lunch, a coffee, or a healthy snack to keep you going, and with outdoor seating on both sides of the building, it’s a perfect spot to study on a nice day, too.']

title: Elmwood Lower for Rent on Delaware Ave
posting_body: ['Lower unit of 2-family within the Historic Delaware District.', 'Steps away from the Rumsey Woods entrance into Delaware Park, offering its walking, running and biking trails, rose garden, scenic Hoyt Lake, Albright Knox Art gallery & more.', "Located just minutes from Elmwood Avenue's shops & restaurants.", 'Updated bathroom with floor to ceiling marble subway wall tile & black marble flooring, claw foot tub with ceiling mounted rain shower head, brass/oil rubbed bronze plumbing fixtures, new toilet and supply/drain lines.', 'Recent kitchen renovation with self-closing cabinetry, washing machine and wine fridge.', 'Lots of natural light, oak hardwood flooring throughout, dining room with coffered ceilings & wood wainscoting, large decorative brick fireplace and large pocket door separating dining room from Fireplace room, which can be used as 3rd bedroom.', 'Two other large bedrooms.', 'Retractable french doors separate the dining from the large living room.', 'Large front lower porch great for people watching.', 'High efficiency washer & dryer in basement.', 'Unit has been primarily owner occupied unit.', 'Other recent upgrades include new drywall ceilings (no popcorn/drop ceilings), new electrical wiring, outlets & panel, spray foam insulation in bathroom, addition off second bedroom, & basement rim joist, new windows in addition & bathroom, freshly painted walls/trim and universal closet systems in each closet.', 'First months rent, security deposit required.', 'All applicants subject to credit inquiry and references.', 'Trash, taxes, water and landscaping paid by landlord.', 'Available September 1st, 2022.']

posting_body: ['2424 Colvin Unit 7  is a beautifully unique 3 BR 1.5 Bath with 2 kitchens and two living spaces.', 'This unit that has been freshly updated with new paint, flooring and cosmetics.', " Located at the foot of the Brighton golf course you couldn't be any closer to this beautiful green space, also just a block from the tops plaza.", 'This beautiful spacious apartment is spread across 2 floors with no one above or below you but yourself.', 'With its own private entrance, the first floor hosts large living room open to kitchen with a large bedroom and large half bath with private laundry hook ups should you desire.', 'Upstairs you find another large living room open to another kitchen, 2 nice sized bedrooms, and a full bath.', 'This unit has 2 parking spaces in the parking lot directly in front of the unit.', 'there is also a rear door to the unit that leads to rear patio.', 'This apartment is more in line with a townhouse than an apartment.', 'The only utilities you will pay are Electric and Cable.', 'Owner Covers Gas bill that feeds heat and hot water.', ' HEAT INCLUDED.', 'This unit would be perfect for someone that has the need for an in law suite, extended family care, personal chef, or someone that has work from home needs.', 'there is also coin operated laundry in the common space of the other units.', 'Please contact shawn via call or text 716 four 9 1 nine 1 0 nine.', '$1950 per month.']

title: 188 Acre Former Cattle Farm in Upstate NY
posting_body: ['Dreaming of starting an organic farm?', "Do you want your own private gentleman/lady's farm?", '188-acre former dairy farm located in upstate NY Otsego County’s Pittsfield, NY just outside New Berlin and Morris, N.Y. with a 2 bedrooms, 2 full-baths, Country Victorian farmhouse with full width covered porch.', 'A short drive to Cooperstown, Norwich, Oneonta and Binghamton and 1.5 hours from the Capital Region.', 'A wonderful mix of open fields, stream, pastures & woods.', '2 story dairy barn across the road with 50 tie stalls, holds 1200 square bales.', 'Multiple storage & out-buildings: 2-car detached garage and equipment shed, roadside stand, hen house, utility shed.', "Enter through the rear Dutch door into a large kitchen opening up to an adjoining ~360 SF family room with wood stove, ceiling fan on 10' tall knotty pine, cathedral ceiling with eat-in dining corner.", 'Off the kitchen is separate oak pantry with two walls of floor-to-ceiling oak cabinets.', 'Walk into the formal dining room with crystal chandelier with window seat and drawer space below.', 'Working oak pocket doors.', 'Living room crowned with a beautiful fireplace and bezel-cut glass door to front porch.', 'Second floor features three large bedrooms with oversized, reach-in closets and a full bath with tub/shower, dual sinks, commode and bidet.', "Walk up to the third floor finished and pellet stove heated ~450 SF attic with 10' cathedral ceiling.", 'Floors are tile, stone, vinyl and hardwood.']

posting_body: ['Welcome to North Buffalo on St. Lawrence.', 'Visit <URL> to book a viewing.', 'This listing is for a first floor, two bedroom 1 bath apartment with electricity included.', 'This unit has been well cared for and updated.', 'Hard wood floors run through both Living room, dining room and bedrooms.', 'Kitchen has new cabinets as well as butcher block counter tops.', 'Stove, refrigerator, and dishwasher are included.', 'A new solar system has been installed for green energy to be supplied by the building owners, keeping electricity included in the rent.', 'Rear of the building has a covered porch with direct access to the right rear bedroom.', 'If you would like this to be your next home, please visit <URL> to start the process.', 'Click on the menu in the top corner of the site, and click on the Rentals tab.', 'You can fill out an application and book a viewing.', 'Applications are subject to minimum credit & income requirements.', 'We look forward to seeing you there!Owner pays for water, sewer, trash, and electricity.', 'Stove, dishwasher and refrigerator are included with washer and dryer hook ups included.', 'Tenant pays gas and internet.', 'No smoking in unit.', 'I will contact you soon@@@@ TEXT::::: (2O1) 5 7 9-1 0 two 4', 'Unique property.', 'Rent Main Apartment only $750.', 'Or rent Main Apartment plus studio and 1 car garage $751.', 'Charming mid century brick home on a corner lot.', '2 bed 1 bath main home.', 'Formal dining room, family room, with fireplace, and large room off the kitchen with built in storage.', 'Central heat and air conditioning.', 'Fenced yard Covered parking.', 'Pets negotiable with additional non refundable 100 fee per pet.', 'No guard dog breeds per insurance.', 'Application back ground and credit check required for all occupants over 18.', 'Non smoking.', 'Detached studio apartment available for increased rent fee.', '$2000 for both house and studio.', 'Deposit $750 if renting both.', 'Shown by appointment only.']
